How can you help me?

5
00:01:48,150 --> 00:01:49,640
As long as you can get rid of him,

6
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:51,519
I'll do whatever you want.

7
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,359
A trade, then.

8
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:56,120
Just help us with one thing.

9
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:04,959
It's you...

