00:40:50,507 --> 00:40:53,267
♪To each other♪

548
00:40:53,741 --> 00:40:56,206
♪If you don't die, I won't stop♪

549
00:40:56,274 --> 00:40:59,053
♪Let's witness together♪

550
00:40:59,157 --> 00:41:02,336
♪The end♪
